      • requestWebPage

        public java.lang.String requestWebPage(ApiUrl apiUrl,
                                       java.lang.String jsonBody,
                                       RequestMethod requestMethod)
        Uses the instance's api key to request information from api.tmdb.org.

        Depending on the autoRetry setting this method will stall and internally recurse until the request was successfully processed.

        Parameters:
        apiUrl - The url to be requested
        jsonBody - can be null
        requestMethod -
